            "description": "Static frame from student's Warmup data transformation appears briefly. Shows items grouped by 2s becoming symbols on a picture graph."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "You started by watching your data transform. Now you can CREATE scaled graphs yourself. You know that each symbol shows 2, and half-symbols show 1."
        },
